  "landing.faq.a1": { en: "We engineered against the AI-look. Pixel-locked keyframes, physics-correct hands, real lighting direction, scene-locked outfits, and natural micro-expressions. Studio outputs are running on Meta and TikTok at $1–3 CPM ranges right now.", "zh-TW": "我們專門對抗 AI 感。像素鎖定關鍵幀、物理正確的手部、真實光線方向、場景鎖定的服裝、自然微表情。Studio 輸出目前在 Meta 與 TikTok 上以 $1–3 CPM 跑量。", de: "Wir haben gegen den AI-Look engineered. Pixel-locked Keyframes, physikalisch korrekte Hände, echte Lichtführung, Scene-locked Outfits, natürliche Mikro-Expressionen. Studio-Outputs laufen auf Meta und TikTok bei $1–3 CPM." },
